Enum Rank

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Rank>
      • edu.ycp.cs201.cards.Rank

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Rank>

    public enum Rank
extends java.lang.Enum<Rank>
    Card rank enumeration. Note that ACE is considered the low rank (because it is the lowest rank in Klondike solitaire).
